      • addKnows

        public boolean addKnows(String fromUser,
               String toUser,
               Integer strength)
                 throws InvalidUserId,
                        UserAlreadyKnowsUser
        Establish a weighted Knows relationship between two users.
        Parameters:
        fromUser - String representation of user establishing the 'knows' relationship
        toUser - String representation of user receiving the 'knows' relationship
        strength - Integer weight of the knows relationship
        Returns:
        true if the relationship was created; false if Strength parameter is null, database error occurred, or if a data model violation was detected.
        Throws:
        InvalidUserId - If either of the user id parameters are invalid
        UserAlreadyKnowsUser - If a 'knows' relationship already exists from fromUser to toUser, or if the user ids are the same.
